name: Efemérides (Module)
body:
### Efemérides (Module)

Efemerides is the module to fit with Efemerides Component.

Support Joomla 1.5, 1.6 and now Joomla! 2.5.

**Important:** The versions 0.9b or greater of the extension are for Joomla! 2.5.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
